# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Urban Resilience Parliament — environment configuration
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to `.env` (same directory) and fill in your own keys.
# `.env` is gitignored — do not commit your real keys.
#
# Two ways to load these:
#   (a) `pip install python-dotenv` → variables auto-loaded by the code
#   (b) `export $(grep -v '^#' .env | xargs)` → bash one-liner
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# === Required: at least ONE chat-completions endpoint ===
#
# OPTION A — zhizengzeng (智增增) aggregator [default, used for HK case data]
#   Single token unlocks 8 frontier LLMs (GPT-5, Claude, Gemini, Grok, Qwen, GLM, Llama, DeepSeek).
#   Sign up: https://zhizengzeng.com — pay-as-you-go, no GFW issues from China.
LLM_BASE_URL=https://api.zhizengzeng.com/v1
LLM_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here

# OPTION B — OpenRouter (https://openrouter.ai)
#   Similar idea: one token, dozens of models. Comment out OPTION A above and use:
# LLM_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1
# LLM_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-...

# OPTION C — OpenAI official (only gives you GPT models)
# LLM_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
# LLM_API_KEY=sk-...

# OPTION D — Anthropic official (Claude only; needs OpenAI-compatible proxy)
#   Use https://github.com/anthropics/anthropic-sdk-python directly, or a
#   shim like https://github.com/jtsang4/claude-to-chatgpt. Not recommended
#   for the 8-LLM parliament — pick A or B.

# === Default model used by `llm_chat()` when caller doesn't specify ===
LLM_MODEL=gpt-5-nano

# === Optional: API key pool (rate-limit spreading) ===
# LLM_API_KEY_POOL=sk-key1,sk-key2,sk-key3

# === Optional: fallback models if primary returns invalid JSON ===
# LLM_FALLBACK_MODELS=gpt-4o-mini,gemini-2.5-flash-lite

# === HTTP / debug ===
LLM_TIMEOUT=60
LLM_DEBUG=0
LLM_LOG_DIR=./logs

# === Optional: Tavily web search (https://tavily.com) ===
#   Used to retrieve recent news / Wikipedia context for the target city.
#   The parliament runs without it (search_context will be empty), but
#   evidence-grounded scoring is markedly stronger with it. Free tier = 1k req/mo.
# TAVILY_API_KEY=tvly-...
# Or rotate multiple:
# TAVILY_KEYS=tvly-key1,tvly-key2
